OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy, with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain this morning, especially in
OL,7,Fthe north. The rain will gradually
OL,8,Ffizzle out to leave a mostly dry
OL,9,Fafternoon. The best of any sunnier
OL,10,Fbreaks most likely seen along the west
OL,11,Fcoast. Feeling rather chilly.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will remain mostly cloudy
OL,14,Fthis evening and overnight, with the
OL,15,Frisk of further patchy rain
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Turning chilly where any
OL,17,Fcloud breaks do occur, with a few fog
OL,18,Fpatches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
