OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy morning, with
OL,6,Fperhaps some light rain in places. The
OL,7,Fcloud may break up a times during the
OL,8,Fafternoon to allow some sunshine
OL,9,Fthrough. Feeling a little milder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FThe
OL,12,Fcloudy theme will continue. It will be
OL,13,Fmostly dry, but some showery rain may
OL,14,Fbe possible at times. Feeling mild
OL,15,Fwhere the cloud breaks and the sun
OL,16,Fcomes out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
